OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FThis evening
OL,6,Fwill be dry with some late sunshine.
OL,7,FThen the rest of the night will be dry
OL,8,Fwith lengthy clear periods and the odd
OL,9,Fmist patch.
OL,10,
OL,11,CThursday:FAll parts will have a dry
OL,12,Fday with plenty of sunshine. Very warm
OL,13,For hot. Light winds.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA dry
OL,16,Fand bright few days although some
OL,17,Fcloud across the north and east at
OL,18,Ftimes. Becoming cooler but still quite
OL,19,Fwarm, especially in the south.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
